After weeks or prototypes, business plans, code reviews we are into the final week. So lets turn to scrum.

&nbsp;
<h2><strong>What is Scrum?</strong></h2>
Scrum is a management and control process that cuts through complexity to focus on building software that meets business needs. Management and teams are able to get their hands around the requirements and technologies, never let go, and deliver working software, incrementally and empirically.

&nbsp;

We are setting the deadline for Wednesday which allows us to develop and finish off everything we need to do before the deadline in a great fashion.
